                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8098" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1260</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2762 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">众望所盼，废然而返——容百科技机构出逃之谜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">What everyone hopes for, but returns in vain——The Mystery of Rongby Technology Institution&#39;s Escape</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宫义飞，夏雪花，金睿洁，满文旭，刘芮彤，戴鸿宇，张鉴彬，李玲娜，廖方楠，李露，李佳奇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宁波容百新能源科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">注册制；企业估值；可持续发展；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">registration system; business valuation; sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鉴于独角兽企业大多存在“风险频发”、“盈余状况虚胖”、“企业估值畸高”等诸多问题，对科创板上市监管政策提出了严峻挑战。本文围绕着注册制下新能源材料公司容百科技科创板上市的估值问题以及上市后的监管，以容百科技逾2亿元的应收账款过期为切入点，以机构出逃作为信号源头，引导学员思考容百科技的价值评估问题，并站在可持续增长的角度评价该企业上市之后的业务创新能力，进一步思考科创板上市条件设立与持续监管应该如何改善？最终提供科创板上市条件设立与持续监管的政策建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In view of the fact that most newly listed enterprises have many problems, such as &quot;frequent risks,&quot; &quot; false and fat earnings status,” and &quot;abnormally high enterprise valuation,&quot; it poses a severe challenge to the listing supervision policy of the Science and Technology Innovation Board. This paper focuses on the valuation of Ronbay Technology, a new energy material listed on the Science and Technology Innovation board under the registration system, and the supervision after the Given that most unicorn companies face many problems such as frequent risks, inflated earnings, and abnormally high valuations, it poses a serious challenge to the regulatory policies for listing on the Science and Technology Innovation Board. This article focuses on the valuation issues and post listing supervision of Rongby Technology Innovation Board, a new energy material company under the registration system. With the expiration of over 200 million yuan in accounts receivable of Rongby Technology as the starting point and institutional escape as the signal source, it guides students to think about the value evaluation of Rongby Technology and evaluates the company&#39;s business innovation ability from the perspective of sustainable growth after listing, How should the conditions for listing on the Science and Technology Innovation Board and continuous supervision be improved? Provide policy recommendations for the establishment of listing conditions and continuous supervision on the Science and Technology Innovation Board.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">独角兽企业估值方法；希金斯理论模型；持续经营三因素理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
